          Publication year
        </th>
        <th>
          GO annotations
        </th>
        <th>
          Phenotypes
        </th>
        <th>
          Protein modifications
        </th>
        <th>
          Gene expression
        </th>
        <th>
          Genetic interactions
        </th>
        <th>
          Physical interactions
